Query Tag Recommendations
The app already applies QUERY_TAG = 'OVERWATCH' with optional detailed tags. Enable detailed tags by default to support:
SQL
-- Cost attribution query
SELECT query_tag, SUM(credits_used_cloud_services) 
FROM SNOWFLAKE.ACCOUNT_USAGE.QUERY_HISTORY
WHERE query_tag ILIKE 'OVERWATCH%'
  AND start_time >= DATEADD('day', -7, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP())
GROUP BY query_tag ORDER BY 2 DESC;
